import React from 'react'
import props from 'prop-types'
import { Box, Card, Image, Heading, Text } from 'rebass'
import logo from '../images/logo512.png'

var projectNames = {"Bunker Down": {projectName:"Bunker Down", projectType:"VideoGame"}}

const ProjectCards = () => {
  return (
      <Box width={256}>
        <Card
          sx={{
            p: 1,
            borderRadius: 2,
            boxShadow: '0 0 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, .25)',
          }}>
          <Image src={logo}/>
          <Box px={2}>
            <Heading as='h3'>
              projectNames["Bunker Down"]
            </Heading>
            <Text fontSize={0}>
              You can edit this code
            </Text>
          </Box>
        </Card>
      </Box>
  )
}

function getProjectCard(projectName) {
  return (
    <Box width={256}>
      <Card
        sx={{
          p: 1,
          borderRadius: 2,
          boxShadow: '0 0 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, .25)',
        }}>
        <Image src={logo}/>
        <Box px={2}>
          <Heading as='h3'>
            name
          </Heading>
          <Text fontSize={0}>
            You can edit this code
          </Text>
        </Box>
      </Card>
    </Box>
  )

}

export default ProjectCards;
